title: DDFP 583: AFC teams not making the playoffs & Dolphins vs. Patriots
itunes:title: DDFP 583: AFC teams not making the playoffs & Dolphins vs. Patriots
description:
Dave Dameshek is joined by Patrick Claybon and Cynthia Frelund to discuss their list of reasons why the New England Patriots won’t end up winning the Super Bowl this year, detailing some of the challenges the team will face. Also, Shek explains why he thinks the Dolphins could potentially win the AFC East in 2017. Then, in the new "Davey Downer" segment, the fellas and Cynthia go division by division predicting which teams in the AFC they believe are definitely not going to make the playoffs this season.
